&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style="font-size: large;"&gt;And if you’re new to these parts, please sign up for the free daily &lt;i&gt;Square&lt;/i&gt; news update &lt;a href="https://www.chicagopublicsquare.com/2017/03/we-didnt-ask-people-to-say-nice-things.html"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
